Legal Staff (Document&Data; Center) - PT Lippo Malls Indonesia
Legal Staff (Document&Data; Center)  -
Legal Staff (Document&Data; Center)
Responsibilities
Filling legal documents all Malls (permit, license, and all kindof agreements)
Monitor expiry date for relevant legal document
Provide administrative support regarding to undergoing legal documents, such as ensuring whereabout legal documents intended to be signed by respective BOD and report progress signing of each required new legal documents
Provide administrative support to distribute (based on level of authority) required legal documents in any project or malls
Requirements
Male / Female, max 28 years old
Candidate must possess at least a Bachelor's Degree Law
Able to communicate in english both oral and written
Able to make agreement letter in English
Able to operating computer especially Microsoft Office
Must be willing to work in Tangerang,Karawaci.
At least 1 year of working experience in Legal Officer or the related field is required for this position
